---
title: Easy Mexican Fiesta Pork & Corn Tacos with Slaw & Spring Onion
description: Sit back and watch the fireworks display of flavour burst through these pork tacos. They’re packed with colourful veggies like corn and carrot garnished with spring onion and the pork is exploding with our Mexican Fiesta spices. To cool off, drizzle over some creamy mayo.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6645b6de2537d3c1a9bdd4cc-92195812.jpeg
